Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.08,0:00:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The man in the alley catches Nell's
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.92,0:00:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,attention the moment she turns the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.52,0:00:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,corner. Unshaven and in tattered
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.08,0:00:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,clothes, he sits on the pavement,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.16,0:00:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,completely drenched from the rain. No
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.12,0:00:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,umbrella, no shelter, just cardboard
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.00,0:00:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,beneath him that has long since turned
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.00,0:00:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,to mush in the downpour.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.03,0:00:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell's heart gives that familiar pang of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,sympathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.96,0:00:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This morning is a cold, gray wash of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.43,0:00:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,misery that seems to seep into her
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.51,0:00:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.67,0:00:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But she is already 15 minutes late for
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.67,0:00:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,her job interview at Morrison and
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.28,0:00:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Associates, clutching her worn portfolio
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.16,0:00:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,against her chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.87,0:00:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She can't afford to be late. Not when
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.28,0:00:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,her rent is already 3 weeks overdue and
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.60,0:00:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,her landlord has started leaving
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.28,0:00:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,increasingly threatening voicemails,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.87,0:00:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,so she has to hurry along. Except
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.44,0:00:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,something about the man makes her pause.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.96,0:00:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Most people in his situation would be
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:01:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,hunched over, trying to make themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,smaller, invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.76,0:01:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This man sits as if he owns the alley.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.68,0:01:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Even sitting on wet pavement in the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.60,0:01:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,pouring rain, there is something almost
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,regal about his posture. His spine is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.04,0:01:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,straight, shoulders squared with a
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.36,0:01:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,dignity that seems completely at odds
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.43,0:01:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,with his circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.40,0:01:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And when he looks up and their eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.15,0:01:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,meet, Nell's breath catches in her
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.56,0:01:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,His gaze is unsettling, not threatening,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.08,0:01:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,but aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.92,0:01:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Too proud for someone who should have
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.52,0:01:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,been broken by whatever circumstances
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.52,0:01:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,have landed him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mostly though, they are the most unusual
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.79,0:01:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,shade of amber she has ever seen. It
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.68,0:01:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,makes her stumble. Her foot catches an
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.43,0:01:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,uneven stone and suddenly she is falling
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.84,0:01:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,forward. Her portfolio flying from her
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.64,0:01:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,grasp.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.88,0:01:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The contents of her purse scatter across
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.04,0:02:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the wet pavement. Her wallet. The
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.68,0:02:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,carefully wrapped sandwich that is
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.36,0:02:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,supposed to be her lunch. Her ancient
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.52,0:02:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Walkman. Every pen she owns.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.00,0:02:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Not again," she whispers, scrambling on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,her hands and knees to collect
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.87,0:02:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,everything before it is ruined or blown
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.95,0:02:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.95,0:02:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when she sees the strange man's
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.72,0:02:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,hands moving alongside hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.23,0:02:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell tenses, expecting him to pocket the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,money. She wouldn't even blame him if he
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.20,0:02:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,did.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.28,0:02:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But instead, he gather her scattered
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.28,0:02:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,belongings with careful precision,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.76,0:02:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,holding everything out to her with a
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.51,0:02:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,gentleness that takes her completely off
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.59,0:02:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,guard. "I believe these are yours," he
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.95,0:02:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,says in a deep voice. He doesn't ask for
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.08,0:02:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,anything in return. He just settles back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.72,0:02:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,against the wall with that same
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.31,0:02:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,inexplicable composure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"Thank you," Nell manages, accepting her
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.72,0:03:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,things with hands that tremble slightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.92,0:03:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The money in her hand represents her bus
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,fair home. The small buffer that might
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.31,0:03:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,let her eat dinner tonight if the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,interview goes as badly as she expects.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, without letting herself think
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.31,0:03:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,too hard about it, she presses the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.56,0:03:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,crumpled bills into his palm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.08,0:03:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,For you, she says softly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.68,0:03:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Get yourself something warm to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The way he looks at her then makes her
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.56,0:03:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,chest tight with an emotion she can't
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,identify,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.48,0:03:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,as if she has just done something
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,extraordinary instead of simply human.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.08,0:03:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,"Thank you," he says quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.59,0:03:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell nods and is about to hurry away to
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.56,0:03:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,rush toward what might be her last
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.31,0:03:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,chance at financial stability.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.92,0:03:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But then she notices the dark stain
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,spreading across the wet pavement where
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.68,0:03:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the man is sitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.31,0:03:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She stops, her heart hammering as she
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:04:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,looks closer. How had she missed it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.79,0:04:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,before?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.87,0:04:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The man may be composed, but now she
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.36,0:04:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,sees what the rain and shadows had
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.20,0:04:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,hidden. His jacket hangs open slightly,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,revealing a dark, wet patch along his
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,ribs where blood seeps through his torn
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.43,0:04:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.43,0:04:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hurt, she exclaims.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The man glances down at his side as if
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,surprised to find it bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.68,0:04:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing, he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He's too pale, Nell thinks, and his lips
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,have taken on a bluish tinge that has
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing to do with the cold rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.24,0:04:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not nothing, she says firmly. You
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,need to get that looked at.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She bites her lip. He obviously can't
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.96,0:04:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,afford a doctor or hospital. That much
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.44,0:04:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,is clear from his circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She thinks of the interview waiting for
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.91,0:04:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,her, of her overdue rent and dwindling
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,options.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:04:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then she looks at this mysterious man
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:05:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,who helped her, all the while bleeding
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,in an alley with nowhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.47,0:05:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,"Come with me," she says, extending her
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,hand. "I can clean that wound and
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.84,0:05:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,bandage it properly."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.40,0:05:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Something flickers across his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet he remains perfectly still, staring
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.63,0:05:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,at her outstretched hand without
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.47,0:05:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,responding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.80,0:05:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The silence stretches uncomfortably.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.91,0:05:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Nell, by the way. Nell days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.28,0:05:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell tries a gentle smile, hoping to
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.44,0:05:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,encourage him. What's yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.12,0:05:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I He starts, then stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,His amber eyes meet hers, and for the
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.91,0:05:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,first time since she's seen him, he
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,looks truly lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't remember, he murmurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.63,0:05:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The rain continues to fall between them
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,as those words hang in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:06:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Chapter 1. You can't remember? Nell
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.84,0:06:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,repeats, staring at him in confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that even mean? His name. The
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.31,0:06:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,last few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants to ask more, but something in
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,his expression, lost and almost fragile,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.31,0:06:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,stops her from pushing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.19,0:06:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's shock from blood loss or
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.75,0:06:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,trauma from whatever gave him that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.44,0:06:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,wound. Either way, standing here
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.03,0:06:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,interrogating an injured man in the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.88,0:06:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,pouring rain isn't helping anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.63,0:06:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, she says gently. We can
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,figure that out later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.88,0:06:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks at her extended hand for
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.72,0:06:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,another long moment before slowly
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.19,0:06:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,reaching out to take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,His fingers are cold despite the earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.47,0:06:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,warmth she'd felt. And she can see the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.03,0:06:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,effort it takes for him to pull himself
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,upright.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.12,0:06:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a pharmacy just around the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.63,0:06:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,corner, she says, leading him out of the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.44,0:07:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,alley. I need to get proper supplies to
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.31,0:07:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,clean that wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.96,0:07:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The pharmacist, a middle-aged woman with
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.28,0:07:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,kind eyes, immediately springs into
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,action.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.96,0:07:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Deep cut? She asks, pulling items from
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.16,0:07:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the shelves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.08,0:07:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll need antiseptic, gauze, medical
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.96,0:07:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,tape, and these waterproof bandages.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Very important to keep it dry once it's
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.16,0:07:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,cleaned. Infection sets in fast with
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.56,0:07:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,wounds like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell nods, watching the growing pile of
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.03,0:07:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,medical supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.44,0:07:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What should he watch for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.75,0:07:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Redness spreading from the wound, red
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.56,0:07:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,streaks, any unusual smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The pharmacist rings up the total.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.24,0:07:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll be $43.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell's stomach drops. She opens her
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.16,0:07:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,wallet, counting the meager bills
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.91,0:07:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,inside. $18.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.12,0:07:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:08:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I She starts, heat flooding her cheeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:08:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I don't have enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.87,0:08:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The pharmacist's expression softens with
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.12,0:08:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.03,0:08:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have anything at home you could
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.47,0:08:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,use instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.87,0:08:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I have hydrogen peroxide, Nell says
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.91,0:08:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,quickly. And rubbing alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.44,0:08:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll work. Just take the bandages
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,then. $12.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.59,0:08:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Relief floods through her as she hands
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.36,0:08:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,over the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Back outside, the nameless man is
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.68,0:08:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,leaning against the pharmacy wall, his
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.16,0:08:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,face even paler than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,"My apartment's only a few blocks away,"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,she says, clutching the small pharmacy
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,bag. "I have everything else we need
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.03,0:08:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,there, and it's warm and dry."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.15,0:08:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks at her with those unsettling
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,amber eyes, and she can see the internal
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,struggle playing across his features.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.32,0:08:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"It's okay," she says. You're hurt and
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm offering help. That's what people
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.27,0:08:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.27,0:09:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Something in her tone seems to decide it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.44,0:09:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,for him. He nods once, a sharp, grateful
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.36,0:09:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,gesture.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Chapter 2. Nell's apartment building is
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,a tired three-story structure that's
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,seen better decades with peeling paint
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and a front door that sticks in humid
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.44,0:09:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.44,0:09:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,As they climb the narrow staircase to
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.36,0:09:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the second floor, she's acutely aware of
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.16,0:09:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,her mysterious companion behind her. The
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,quiet way he moves, how he seems to take
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.48,0:09:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,in every detail of their surroundings
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.56,0:09:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,with those unsettling amber eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.48,0:09:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,On the landing, they encounter Mr.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoffman from 1B, standing in his pajamas
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.12,0:09:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and slippers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.88,0:09:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"Oh, hello, dear," he says to Nell,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.76,0:09:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,blinking owlishly. I was just
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to get milk for my coffee, but I
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.56,0:09:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,can't remember where I put my keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.83,0:09:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell's heart sinks. This is the third
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.56,0:10:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,time this week she's found him like
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.08,0:10:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.08,0:10:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hoffman, you're not dressed. Let's
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.64,0:10:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,get you back inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.88,0:10:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not. He looks genuinely surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.51,0:10:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The stranger steps forward, gently
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.83,0:10:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,taking Mr. Hoffman's other arm, helping
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.56,0:10:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,guide the elderly man back toward his
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.56,0:10:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,apartment door.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,"Strange?" he murmurs so quietly only
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.07,0:10:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell can hear. "What's strange?" she
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.76,0:10:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,whispers back. "The smell? Can't you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.80,0:10:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He trails off, shaking his head. "Never
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.27,0:10:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,mind."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell doesn't smell anything unusual,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.44,0:10:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,just the typical musty odor of an old
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.60,0:10:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,building.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.68,0:10:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Once they've settled Mr. Hoffman safely
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.92,0:10:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,in his apartment, Nell leads her guest
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,down to her own door.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.51,0:10:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Her hands shake slightly as she fumbles
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.60,0:10:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,with her keys and suddenly the reality
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.16,0:10:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,of what she's doing hits her like a
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.07,0:11:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,physical blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.48,0:11:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Her apartment suddenly feels impossibly
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,small.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.48,0:11:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The stranger seems to fill the entire
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,living room just by standing there. this
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.12,0:11:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,tall, broad shouldered man with dirt
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.20,0:11:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,under his fingernails and stubble that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,could hide any number of scars.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.72,0:11:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What if he's dangerous? What if helping
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,him was the stupidest thing she's ever
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.44,0:11:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,done? The stranger seems to sense her
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.39,0:11:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,sudden tension. He stops just inside her
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.36,0:11:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,doorway, keeping his distance, his hands
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.92,0:11:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,visible and open at his sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.95,0:11:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can go, he says quietly, his voice
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,gentle, unthreatening. The way he's
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.72,0:11:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,giving her an out makes her feel guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A dangerous man wouldn't do that, would
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.12,0:11:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,he? No, she says, shaking her head
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,firmly. You're hurt, and there's a storm
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.76,0:11:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,coming. She opens the door wider,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.80,0:11:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,gesturing him inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Her apartment is small but clean, a
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,living room that doubles as her
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:12:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,workspace, a tiny kitchen, and a bedroom
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,barely big enough for her twin bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.72,0:12:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But before I look at that wound, she
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.27,0:12:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,says, taking in his rain soaked, dirty
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,clothes that are leaving wet spots on
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,her hardwood floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.07,0:12:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to clean up. If I bandage you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.95,0:12:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,like this, you'll definitely get an
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,infection.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.36,0:12:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She disappears into her bedroom and
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.27,0:12:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,returns with an armful of men's
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.95,0:12:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,clothing, jeans, a sweater, clean
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.60,0:12:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,underwear, and socks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.48,0:12:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,These belonged to my ex-boyfriend, she
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.27,0:12:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,explains. He left them here when he
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.36,0:12:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,moved in with our colleague. His loss is
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,your gain, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The stranger takes the clothes with a
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.56,0:12:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,grateful nod.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.88,0:12:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Bathrooms through there, she says,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.04,0:12:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,pointing. There's shampoo, soap, clean
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,towels. I even have an unused razor and
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.72,0:12:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,shaving cream if you want them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,While he showers, Nell listens to the
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.76,0:12:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,sound of running water and trs not to
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.32,0:13:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,think about the fact that there's a
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.68,0:13:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,naked stranger in her bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.95,0:13:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She tries calling Morrison and
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.56,0:13:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,associates to reschedule her interview,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but the receptionist barely lets her
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.88,0:13:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,finish explaining before hanging up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.48,0:13:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's that job opportunity gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,20 minutes later, the bathroom door
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,opens with a soft click, and when Nell
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.92,0:13:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,turns around, her breath catches.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.83,0:13:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Clean shaven and fresh from the shower,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the stranger is stunning, breathtaking
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.16,0:13:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,in a way that knocks the air from her
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,lungs. How had she not noticed before
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.07,0:13:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,that he has features like something out
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.68,0:13:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,of a Renaissance statue?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.95,0:13:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She stares a moment too long, heat
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.27,0:13:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,creeping up her neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, she says, voice a little horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.27,0:13:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get that cleaned up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.07,0:13:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The wound is worse than she thought. A
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,deep, clean puncture with bruising
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:14:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,around the edges.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:14:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This looks like a stab wound, she says,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.32,0:14:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,keeping her voice steady as she applies
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,hydrogen peroxide.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.72,0:14:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,When did this happen? She asks, blotting
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.92,0:14:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the blood with a cloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.72,0:14:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A couple hours ago, he replies, voice
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,tight with controlled pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.19,0:14:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Some men were displeased that I'd chosen
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,their spot to wait out the rain. One had
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.72,0:14:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,a knife. Things escalated quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell pauses. They stabbed you over a
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.36,0:14:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,place to sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.19,0:14:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,When territory is all you have, he says
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.32,0:14:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,quietly, eyes steady on hers. No matter
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.51,0:14:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,how small you defend it, the wound is
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.07,0:14:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,finally clean. She applies antibiotic
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.04,0:14:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,ointment. Careful and slow. He flinches
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,slightly. You should really see a
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.88,0:14:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This will have to do, he says simply.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.32,0:14:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Outside, the storm swells.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:15:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He glances at the window, then at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.92,0:15:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay, she says firmly, smoothing down
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.16,0:15:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the last strip of tape. At least until
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the storm passes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He studies her amber eyes unreadable,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,then nods.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.07,0:15:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Just until the storm passes, he agrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.51,0:15:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,As if on Q, thunder rolls overhead like
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.24,0:15:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,a freight train and the lights flicker.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.56,0:15:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Chapter 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.04,0:15:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That night, Nell lies awake listening to
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the storm rage outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Every creek of the old building makes
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.32,0:15:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,her hyper aware of the stranger sleeping
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,on her couch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.39,0:15:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, he looks like a fallen angel, but
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.36,0:15:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that doesn't mean he couldn't strangle
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.80,0:15:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,her in her sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.36,0:15:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She must eventually drift off because
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,she finds herself dreaming of padding to
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.92,0:15:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the bathroom in the middle of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.07,0:15:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And instead of the stranger, there's a
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.56,0:15:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,massive wolf stretched across her couch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.80,0:16:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The creature is enormous, sleeping
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.04,0:16:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,peacefully with its head resting on the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.88,0:16:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,armrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Even in sleep, there's something
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.32,0:16:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,majestic about it, something that seems
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.80,0:16:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,both wild and strangely familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.80,0:16:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She wonders distantly why she's not
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.72,0:16:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,afraid of finding a giant wolf in her
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.80,0:16:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.95,0:16:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What a weird dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.27,0:16:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The next morning, the storm is still
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,battering the windows when Nell emerges
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.19,0:16:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,from her bedroom. "Good morning," her
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.16,0:16:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,guest says, turning to offer her a
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.16,0:16:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,steaming mug. "I hope you don't mind. I
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,made coffee."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,"No, that's great," she says, accepting
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the cup gratefully. "You didn't have to
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.75,0:16:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She studies his face in the morning
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.51,0:16:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,light. Clean shaven and rested, he looks
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.63,0:16:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,even more striking than he had the night
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.48,0:16:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.72,0:16:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something almost aristocratic
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.63,0:16:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,about the way he holds himself, even in
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.27,0:17:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,her ex-boyfriend's borrowed clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.63,0:17:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,"Are you hungry?" she asks. "I could
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.07,0:17:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,make breakfast."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.07,0:17:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,As she moves around the kitchen pulling
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.83,0:17:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,out eggs and bacon, she notices him
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.64,0:17:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,examining her small bookshelf.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.91,0:17:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Her collection isn't extensive, mostly
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.48,0:17:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,secondhand paperbacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.64,0:17:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The brother's Karamazoff, he says,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,touching the spine of one book. Nell
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,pauses, spatula in hand. Have you read
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.40,0:17:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,it? His brow furrows in concentration.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.40,0:17:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so. I remember enjoying it. So,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,you do remember some things? Nell
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.79,0:17:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,observes carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.67,0:17:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The question seems to pain him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really. Nothing beyond waking up
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.03,0:17:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,alone in an alley about 2 months ago, he
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,says. I don't know how I got there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe a head injury, Nell suggests
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.12,0:17:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,gently.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.64,0:17:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no injuries when I woke up, he
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.03,0:18:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,replies. Just emptiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.76,0:18:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks back at the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.24,0:18:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first thing that feels a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.91,0:18:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,familiar to me. I remember particularly
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.20,0:18:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,liking one of the characters, Dimmitri.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.96,0:18:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He was passionate, conflicted, but
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.40,0:18:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,ultimately redeemable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell's heart aches for him. Then that
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.24,0:18:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,should be your name, she says
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.32,0:18:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,impulsively.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,until you remember your real one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.32,0:18:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Dimmitri.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.72,0:18:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Dimmitri, he repeats slowly. That's
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.79,0:18:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,acceptable, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell can't help but laugh at his prim
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.84,0:18:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.67,0:18:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Dimmitri suddenly goes rigid, his head
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.24,0:18:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,snapping up like he's heard something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.36,0:18:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,"What's wrong?" Nell asks, turning off
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.08,0:18:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the burner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.84,0:18:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't answer, instead rising and
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.32,0:18:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,moving to the center of the room,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,nostrils flaring slightly as he sniffs
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.55,0:19:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.48,0:19:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,"Can't you smell that?" he asks
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.96,0:19:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,urgently.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.48,0:19:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell inhales deeply. "Smell what?" "The
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.91,0:19:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,bacon."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.91,0:19:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"No," he says. "Something's wrong."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.52,0:19:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Before she can respond, he bolts for the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.60,0:19:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,door. "What the heck?" Nell mutters,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.60,0:19:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,following him into the hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.72,0:19:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She spots from halfway down the stairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to force open a door on the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.40,0:19:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,ground floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.79,0:19:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's locked, she calls down to him. It
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.67,0:19:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,leads to the boiler room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.79,0:19:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Dimmitri ignores her, throwing his
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.96,0:19:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulder against the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.67,0:19:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stop," Nell says, hurrying down the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.48,0:19:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,stairs. "You need a" The door gives way
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.84,0:19:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,with a loud crack, and Dimmitri
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,disappears inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.24,0:19:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell stares at the broken door frame in
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.32,0:19:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"What are you doing?" she calls,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.48,0:19:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,following him into the basement. "I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.64,0:20:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,going to get in trouble with my
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.67,0:20:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,landlord."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.00,0:20:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The basement is dark and cramped, filled
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.48,0:20:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,with the building's ancient heating
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.16,0:20:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,system. She can see Dimmitri near the
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.88,0:20:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,boiler, examining something with intense
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.60,0:20:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,"Seriously, you can't be here." She
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.20,0:20:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,tries again, starting down the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.24,0:20:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay back, he orders. There's a leak.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.60,0:20:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't stay in here. It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Nell lets him drag her back up the
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.32,0:20:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,stairs. What kind of leak?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.08,0:20:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Carbon monoxide, Dimmetry says, pulling
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.03,0:20:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,her toward the building's exit. We need
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.67,0:20:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,to call 911 now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I have a phone upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.60,0:20:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He's already dragging her outside into
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the storm. Rain immediately soaking
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.15,0:20:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,through their clothes. The nearest cafe
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.12,0:20:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is half a block away, but Dimmitri seems
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.91,0:21:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,to know exactly where he's going.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency. He tells the barista tursley.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.72,0:21:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to use your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,20 minutes later, Nell watches from
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.08,0:21:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,across the street as firefighters stream
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.40,0:21:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,into her building.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.79,0:21:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The fire chief confirms a significant
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.88,0:21:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,gas leak in the basement and carbon
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.12,0:21:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,monoxide has been seeping into the
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.88,0:21:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,building for weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.67,0:21:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't know how you figured it out. One
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,of them tells Dmitri.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Carbon monoxide has no smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.52,0:21:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dmitri looks like he's about to disagree
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.44,0:21:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,when Nell's landlord, Mr. Ke, arrives
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.32,0:21:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,looking harried and annoyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.52,0:21:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,"What's all this about?" he demands,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.15,0:21:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,glaring at Nell. Did you cause this
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.55,0:21:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,mess?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.72,0:21:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a gas leak, Nell explains. It
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.91,0:21:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,could have killed people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.32,0:21:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The ventilation system just needs a good
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,kick. Keep mutters, then catches
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.72,0:22:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.32,0:22:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you're all overreacting.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.08,0:22:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Dimmitri steps forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.64,0:22:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew. His voice is cold, precise.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.20,0:22:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew there was a problem with the
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.72,0:22:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,ventilation and you did nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.76,0:22:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep takes a step back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.32,0:22:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now see here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.32,0:22:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a responsibility to maintain
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.24,0:22:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,safe living conditions. Dimmitri
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.88,0:22:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,continues, his tone sharp. The lack of
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.00,0:22:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,proper gas detection and ventilation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.08,0:22:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,maintenance is a clear violation of
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.91,0:22:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,housing codes. People could have died.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.72,0:22:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hoffman has been getting confused
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.40,0:22:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and sick. Nell interrupts, the pieces
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.52,0:22:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,clicking together. That's why he's been
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.15,0:22:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,so disoriented. He's been slowly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.64,0:22:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,poisoning himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.52,0:22:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Keeps face goes pale. Look, nobody needs
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.79,0:22:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to make this into a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.44,0:22:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to be hearing from my
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.03,0:22:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,attorneys, Dimmitri says flatly, his
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.64,0:23:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,voice carrying a threat that makes even
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.72,0:23:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell shiver. Negligent endangerment,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.55,0:23:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,violation of housing codes. Wait, Keep
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.32,0:23:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,says desperately. Maybe we can work
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.48,0:23:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,something out. How about three free
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.64,0:23:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,months rent?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.20,0:23:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're joking, Dimmitri cuts him off,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.67,0:23:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,his amber eyes blazing. You endangered
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.55,0:23:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,lives through criminal negligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.15,0:23:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Dimmitri, Nell says quietly, placing a
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.44,0:23:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,gentle hand on his arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.08,0:23:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I talk to you for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.96,0:23:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She can feel the tension radiating from
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.96,0:23:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,him, but he allows her to pull him
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.28,0:23:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.60,0:23:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, she says in a low voice, "I
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.52,0:23:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,appreciate what you're doing, but nobody
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.67,0:23:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,here can afford lawyers. Certainly not
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.00,0:23:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,you."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.00,0:23:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Dimmitri mouth opens like he's about to
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.15,0:23:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,protest. Then it closes and he blinks
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.64,0:23:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,like he's only just remembered that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.32,0:23:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,fact. "That's not the point," he says
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.08,0:24:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,eventually. "He can't be allowed to get
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.24,0:24:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,away with this." "He's not getting away
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.72,0:24:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,with it," Nell says firmly. He's
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.44,0:24:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,offering 3 months free rent for
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.28,0:24:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone. That's real help right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.40,0:24:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is safe thanks to you. That's
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.32,0:24:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,what matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.64,0:24:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She watches him wrestle with this. Sees
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.36,0:24:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the moment when his rigid posture starts
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.67,0:24:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,to relax slightly. The hard edges of his
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.79,0:24:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,authority soften and he looks almost
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.12,0:24:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,vulnerable again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.84,0:24:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you really, Dimmitri? Nell
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.32,0:24:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,wonders, watching him stare pensively
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.55,0:24:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,out at the storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.20,0:24:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Chapter 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.52,0:24:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Later that evening, when the fire
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.36,0:24:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,department finally gives the allclear,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.08,0:24:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell and Dmitri climb the stairs to her
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.48,0:24:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,apartment in companionable silence. "Let
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.76,0:24:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,me check your wound," Nell says once
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.08,0:24:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,they're inside. Dmitri nods, settling
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.36,0:24:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,onto the couch and lifting the borrowed
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.12,0:24:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,sweater.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.79,0:24:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell kneels beside him, her fingers
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.20,0:25:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,working to carefully peel back the
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.03,0:25:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,bandage.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.03,0:25:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then she freezes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.44,0:25:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's That's not possible, she
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.08,0:25:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,whispers.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.76,0:25:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the deep puncture wound had been
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.60,0:25:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,just the night before, there's now only
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.15,0:25:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,smooth, unmarked skin. Not even a scar
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.00,0:25:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.32,0:25:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand, Dimmitri says,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.84,0:25:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,staring down at his own torso with the
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.84,0:25:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,same bewilderment she feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.12,0:25:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell runs her finger lightly over the
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.20,0:25:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,spot where the wound had been.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.32,0:25:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I was worried about infection, about you
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.96,0:25:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,needing stitches,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.36,0:25:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,she murmurs more to herself than to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.36,0:25:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it wasn't as deep as we thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.84,0:25:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Dimmitri suggests, but his voice lacks
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.72,0:25:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,conviction.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.79,0:25:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe, Nell agrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.44,0:25:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They stare at each other in the
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.72,0:25:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,lamplight, sharing a moment of mutual
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.36,0:25:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.76,0:26:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But the confusion fades, and as the
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.76,0:26:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,silence stretches between them, Nell
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.24,0:26:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes acutely aware of how close they
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.48,0:26:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,are.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.40,0:26:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How she's still kneeling beside him on
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.15,0:26:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the couch, her hand resting on his bare
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.55,0:26:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.48,0:26:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Her breath catches when he lifts his
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.24,0:26:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,hand, his fingers hovering just above
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.64,0:26:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,her cheek. Then reality crashes back in.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.79,0:26:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.79,0:26:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Dimmitri pulls his sweater back down,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.96,0:26:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,standing abruptly.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.36,0:26:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, she repeats.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.15,0:26:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm better, he says. You've been more
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.20,0:26:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,than kind, but I should give you your
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.88,0:26:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,space back.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.72,0:26:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell feels a strange urge to protest, to
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.91,0:26:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,find reasons why he should stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.20,0:26:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But none of them make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.60,0:26:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right. He's healed. the crisis is
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.88,0:26:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,over and she has no real reason to ask
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.36,0:26:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,him to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.60,0:27:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,"Of course," she says instead, forcing a
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.03,0:27:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,smile. "Let me pack you some food."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.03,0:27:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,When she returns to the living room,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.03,0:27:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Dimmitri is folding his old clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.52,0:27:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,"Keep those," she says, nodding toward
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.40,0:27:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the clothes he's wearing. "They fit you
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.72,0:27:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,better anyway."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.79,0:27:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,"Are you sure?" "Trust me, I never want
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.32,0:27:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,to see them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.24,0:27:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The bitterness in her voice surprises
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.24,0:27:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,them both.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.64,0:27:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Dimmitri takes the bag of food, his
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.20,0:27:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,fingers brushing hers as he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.79,0:27:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,"Thank you," he says quietly. "For
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.64,0:27:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.15,0:27:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,your kindness, your home. I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.60,0:27:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,how to repay you."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.84,0:27:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"It was nothing," Nell assures him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.36,0:27:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"No,"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.88,0:27:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Dimmitri tells her. And there's
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.20,0:27:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,something almost fierce in his voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.24,0:27:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't nothing. You helped a stranger
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.72,0:27:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,when you had every reason not to. You
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.27,0:27:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,shared your food, your home, your
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.36,0:28:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.67,0:28:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He pauses, troubled.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.15,0:28:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember who I was before, but I
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.79,0:28:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,don't think I was kind. I don't think I
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.88,0:28:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,would have done what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.60,0:28:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And then he's gone, leaving her standing
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.24,0:28:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,in her suddenly too quiet apartment,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.79,0:28:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,staring at the empty couch where he'd
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.55,0:28:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,slept.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.67,0:28:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Chapter 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.24,0:28:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Two days pass in a blur of ordinary
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.48,0:28:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,routine that somehow feels completely
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.72,0:28:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.64,0:28:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell goes to job interviews, comes home
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.12,0:28:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to her empty apartment, and tries to
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.60,0:28:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,pretend she doesn't keep glancing at the
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.44,0:28:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,couch where Dimmitri had slept.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.79,0:28:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She tells herself it's ridiculous. She
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.60,0:28:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,knew him for less than 48 hours. People
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.79,0:28:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,don't form attachments that quickly to
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.72,0:28:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,complete strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.60,0:28:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But then the storm hits. It starts as
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.55,0:28:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,heavy rain around noon, the kind that
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.03,0:28:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,makes the city's inadequate drainage
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.79,0:29:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,systems overflow and turn streets into
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.44,0:29:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,rivers.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.67,0:29:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,By evening, it's upgraded to something
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.91,0:29:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,apocalyptic. Howling winds that rattle
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.88,0:29:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,her windows, hail the size of golf
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.20,0:29:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,balls, and rain so heavy she can barely
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.76,0:29:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,see the building across the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.12,0:29:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell paces her apartment, checking the
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.60,0:29:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,weather reports obsessively.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.15,0:29:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,All she can think about is Dimmitri
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.64,0:29:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,somewhere out there in this nightmare
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.32,0:29:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,weather with nothing but the clothes on
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.00,0:29:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.32,0:29:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,By 10:00, she can't stand it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.67,0:29:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She pulls on her heaviest coat, grabs an
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.48,0:29:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,umbrella, and ventures out into the
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.15,0:29:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.24,0:29:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind nearly knocks her over the
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.91,0:29:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,moment she steps outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.55,0:29:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The streets are almost completely
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.32,0:29:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,deserted, except for the occasional
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.24,0:29:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,emergency vehicle racing past with
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.39,0:29:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,sirens wailing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.27,0:29:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Water rushes down the gutters like
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.12,0:29:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,rapids, and she has to hold on to
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.27,0:29:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,building walls to keep from being swept
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.20,0:30:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,away.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.20,0:30:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She makes it to the alley where she
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.79,0:30:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,first found him. Empty except for debris
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.67,0:30:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,blown in by the wind. Where would he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.36,0:30:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Where could anyone go in this?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.72,0:30:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She's about to give up, soaked to the
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.88,0:30:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,bone and shivering violently when she
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.27,0:30:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,spots a figure huddled in a narrow al
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.44,0:30:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,cove between two buildings.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.48,0:30:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Dimmitri, she calls out, fighting to be
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.03,0:30:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,heard over the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.27,0:30:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks up and even through the rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.67,0:30:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,she can see his surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.08,0:30:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,"Nel."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.76,0:30:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They share a look across the storm
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.67,0:30:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,lashed space between them. "You're still
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.72,0:30:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,here," she says, gesturing to the area
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.67,0:30:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,near where she'd first found him. A
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.55,0:30:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,small smile tugs at the corner of his
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.64,0:30:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.39,0:30:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,"Well, I thought just in case."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.44,0:30:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The way he says it makes her chest
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.03,0:30:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.72,0:30:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Just in case of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.12,0:30:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,In case she came looking for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.91,0:31:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The possibility that he might have been
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.91,0:31:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,hoping sends warmth flooding through her
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.32,0:31:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,despite the cold rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.03,0:31:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back with me, she says impulsively.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.24,0:31:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, you can't stay out here in this
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.48,0:31:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.64,0:31:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.24,0:31:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,what if there's another gas leak? She
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.64,0:31:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,interrupts. What if I need someone with
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.12,0:31:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,a super smell to save the building?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.55,0:31:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,super smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.48,0:31:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Dimmitri looks like he's fighting
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.91,0:31:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,another smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.39,0:31:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A particularly strong gust of wind sends
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.88,0:31:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,debris flying past them. His hand comes
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.00,0:31:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,up to steady her, fingers gentle but
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.64,0:31:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,firm on her arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.44,0:31:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The storm's getting worse, she says
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.84,0:31:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.51,0:31:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to sleep knowing you're
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.27,0:31:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.44,0:31:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks at her for a long moment, rain
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.84,0:31:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,dripping from his dark hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.88,0:31:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,"You don't even know me," he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.00,0:32:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,"That's not true," she protests. And the
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.36,0:32:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,admission feels heavier than it should.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.24,0:32:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"You're
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.84,0:32:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,you're my friend." "Come home with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.79,0:32:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Dimmitri," she says softly. Just until
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.64,0:32:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the storm passes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.44,0:32:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He nods finally, and she feels relief
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.91,0:32:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,flood through her so strongly it's
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.76,0:32:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,almost dizzying.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.08,0:32:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just until the storm passes, he agrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.03,0:32:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Chapter 6. Back in her apartment, they
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.64,0:32:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,stand dripping in her small entryway.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.15,0:32:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,"I should get you a towel," Nell says,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.08,0:32:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,accutely aware of how his wet clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.15,0:32:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,cling to his frame.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.96,0:32:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be good, Dimmitri agrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.39,0:32:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She bustles around, gathering dry
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.72,0:32:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,clothes and towels, trying to ignore the
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.27,0:32:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,way her pulse quickens.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.15,0:32:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just You can change, she says,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.08,0:33:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,gesturing toward the bedroom. I'll go
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.79,0:33:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,get some sleep. You should, too. It's
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.79,0:33:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,late.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.96,0:33:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he agrees, but makes no move toward
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.24,0:33:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the makeshift bed. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.48,0:33:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They stand there in her small living
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.15,0:33:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,room, the weight of unspoken things
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.39,0:33:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,pressing down on them. "Well," Nell says
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.91,0:33:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,finally, "Good night." She escapes to
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.72,0:33:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,her bedroom, but sleep is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.51,0:33:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Not with him on the other side of the
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.20,0:33:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,wall. Every creek, every shift of the
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.79,0:33:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,couch, every breath he takes sounds like
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.76,0:33:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it's right next to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.48,0:33:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,After what feels like an hour, she gives
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.48,0:33:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.08,0:33:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,barefoot, she creeps to the door and
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.24,0:33:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,presses her ear against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.36,0:33:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.12,0:33:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She eases it open and peaks out. The
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.15,0:33:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,living room is washed in moonlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.88,0:33:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Dimmitri is sitting on the edge of the
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.55,0:33:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,couch, elbows on his knees, staring out
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.96,0:34:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the window,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.36,0:34:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,still watchful, like he's hunting
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.24,0:34:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,something in the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.20,0:34:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't sleep either, she whispers.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.79,0:34:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He turns his head toward her voice. Even
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.28,0:34:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,in the dark, his eyes gleam.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.63,0:34:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,"No," he says softly.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.83,0:34:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She steps out, suddenly too aware of her
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.63,0:34:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,thin night gown and bare legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.67,0:34:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,"The air feels colder, her skin
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.07,0:34:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,tighter."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.07,0:34:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,"I thought maybe I'd make some tea."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.07,0:34:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,"Camomile,"
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.67,0:34:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,she says, trying to sound casual. "It
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.56,0:34:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,helps sometimes."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.04,0:34:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Help,"
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.72,0:34:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,he repeats, and there's something darkly
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.28,0:34:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,amused in his tone.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.91,0:34:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She clears her throat. "Would you like
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.80,0:34:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,some?" She's already reaching for the
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.28,0:34:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,kettle when she hears him stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.83,0:34:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Footsteps behind her, slow, controlled,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.48,0:35:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,not loud, but present. And when she
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.68,0:35:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,turns, he is here. She backs up
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.07,0:35:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,instinctively, the counter pressing into
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.48,0:35:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,her lower back. He follows, stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.07,0:35:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,just shy of touching her. "Nel," he
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.80,0:35:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,murmurs, his voice like smoke, rough and
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.88,0:35:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,intimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.88,0:35:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She wets her lips. His head dips lower,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.16,0:35:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and she feels the brush of his nose
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.83,0:35:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,against her throat. "I don't want tea,"
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.96,0:35:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,he murmurs, lips grazing her skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.24,0:35:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She swallows.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.00,0:35:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"No," she asks.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.04,0:35:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Her hands fly to his chest, meant to
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.35,0:35:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,push, but they don't. They curl into his
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.07,0:35:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,shirt instead, pulling him closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.52,0:35:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You smell like rain and heat, he
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.76,0:35:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,replies. And something sweeter
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.76,0:35:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,underneath,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.16,0:35:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Dimmitri, she breathes, her whole body
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.72,0:35:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,thrumming.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.48,0:35:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been so kind to me, he whispers.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.52,0:35:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me make it up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.32,0:35:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The kiss crashes over them like the
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.07,0:36:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,storm outside. Hungry, reckless,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.64,0:36:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,overdue.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.40,0:36:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He kisses her like he's remembering
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.24,0:36:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,something with his body before his mind
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.00,0:36:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,can catch up. Like her mouth is a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.88,0:36:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,he's known in another life. And the tea
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.83,0:36:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,is forgotten entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.20,0:36:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Chapter 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.28,0:36:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell wakes to the low clink of ceramic
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.83,0:36:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and the soft hiss of a stovetop flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.35,0:36:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She pads barefoot into the kitchen, the
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.16,0:36:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,cotton of her night gown clinging to
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.00,0:36:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,sleepwarmed skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.96,0:36:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Dimmitri stands at the stove barefoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.24,0:36:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When he turns to look at her, his amber
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.64,0:36:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,eyes glow in the morning light, and his
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.20,0:36:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,slow, lazy smile nearly brings her to
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.83,0:36:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,her knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.00,0:36:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,"Morning," he rumbles, voice still thick
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.11,0:36:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,from sleep. "Morning," she says,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.32,0:36:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly shy. He hands her a mug,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.68,0:36:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,fingers brushing hers, and her stomach
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.68,0:36:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,flutters. a soft, nervous excitement she
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.44,0:37:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,hasn't felt since she was a teenager.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.83,0:37:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The storm's over, she murmurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.20,0:37:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So it is, he says, eyes focused on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.88,0:37:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You could stay another day. She
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.44,0:37:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,hesitates
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.04,0:37:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,just to be safe. The forecast mentioned
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.68,0:37:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,possible
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.20,0:37:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,aftershocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.76,0:37:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A beat of silence, then his mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.00,0:37:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,twitches.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.68,0:37:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Aftershocks, he echoes, stepping forward
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.88,0:37:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,with a glint in his eyes. I see. You're
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.72,0:37:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,just being responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.11,0:37:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I am extremely responsible, she replies,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.07,0:37:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,chin lifting.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.24,0:37:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he agrees, his voice rough as his
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.92,0:37:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,fingers tuck a strand of hair behind her
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.00,0:37:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.83,0:37:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You are. When he kisses her, it's slow
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.35,0:37:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and warm, tasting like coffee and
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.92,0:37:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,something deeper. something unspoken.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.68,0:37:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Her body leans into him before her mind
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.24,0:38:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,catches up. Just one more day, he
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.59,0:38:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,murmurs against her lips. But one day
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.07,0:38:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes two, then a week, then more.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.40,0:38:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They fall into an easy rhythm, except
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.80,0:38:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing about it is easy. Every brush of
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.00,0:38:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,skin feels electric.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.40,0:38:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Every look lingers a beat too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.07,0:38:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I am just grateful," he says one
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.64,0:38:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,afternoon, backing her against the
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.24,0:38:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,counter, his mouth ghosting her jaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.92,0:38:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"You saved my life. Let me show my
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.56,0:38:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,appreciation."
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.88,0:38:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,"This is appreciation," she pants as his
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.92,0:38:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,fingers tease the edge of her waistband.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.11,0:38:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,"Deep, soultering gratitude," he
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.56,0:38:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,confirms solemnly before kneeling to
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.28,0:38:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,demonstrate just how grateful he can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.04,0:38:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They joke about their arrangement. Nell
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.44,0:38:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,calling him her kept man. Dimmitri
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.24,0:38:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,insisting he's earning his keep in
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.32,0:38:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,increasingly creative ways. But
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.35,0:39:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,underneath the humor is something
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.04,0:39:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,deeper, more intense,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.48,0:39:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,like the way his eyes go flat and
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.56,0:39:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,predatory when another man flirts with
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.48,0:39:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,her at the corner store.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.20,0:39:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,or the way he growls low and quiet when
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.88,0:39:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,he kisses her neck just where her pulse
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.44,0:39:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,beats loudest.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.92,0:39:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,"You're insatiable," she gasps one night
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.04,0:39:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,as he presses her into the couch
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.56,0:39:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,cushions.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.32,0:39:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,"For you," he breathes, voice rough with
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.16,0:39:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,need. "Only ever for you."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.11,0:39:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Dimmitri isn't content to simply live in
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.52,0:39:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,her space. He approaches her apartment's
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.40,0:39:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,problems with systematic efficiency. He
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.20,0:39:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't just fix the cabinet door. He
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.52,0:39:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,reorganizes the entire kitchen for
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.83,0:39:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,optimal workflow.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.72,0:39:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to do all this. Nell says
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.24,0:39:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,she's holding a screwdriver he handed
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.00,0:39:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,her without explanation, standing on a
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.56,0:40:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,chair to reach a light fixture.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.83,0:40:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's inefficient to let problems
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.76,0:40:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,accumulate, he says matterofactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.88,0:40:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Small issues become systemic failures.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.72,0:40:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon, Dimmitri's organizational skills
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.96,0:40:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,extend beyond her apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.92,0:40:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He creates schedules for building
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.59,0:40:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,maintenance, rotation charts for helping
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.00,0:40:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Chen that somehow get implemented
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.07,0:40:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,without anyone quite remembering
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.83,0:40:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,agreeing to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.40,0:40:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a way with people, Nell
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.72,0:40:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,observes one evening as they climb the
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.48,0:40:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.32,0:40:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like you always know how to get
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.00,0:40:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,them to do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.88,0:40:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Dimmitri stops so suddenly she nearly
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.88,0:40:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,collides with him. "Is that a bad
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.52,0:40:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,thing?" he asks, genuinely curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.44,0:40:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,"No," she says, accutely aware of his
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.48,0:40:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,fingers on her elbow. "It's just
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.72,0:40:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,unusual."
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.11,0:40:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, when they're tangled in bed, he
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.52,0:40:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,kisses down her neck with barely
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.35,0:41:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,restrained hunger.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.52,0:41:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She feels his teeth graze her skin,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.56,0:41:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,sharper than they should be. Something
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.20,0:41:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,in his voice is trembling.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.83,0:41:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't. Instead, he sinks his mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.96,0:41:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,into her skin and leaves bruises shaped
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.04,0:41:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,like his hunger.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.44,0:41:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,One afternoon at their usual coffee
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.35,0:41:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,shop, Nell excuses herself for the
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.68,0:41:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,bathroom. When she returns, she finds a
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.96,0:41:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,woman leaning against their table
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.96,0:41:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,talking to Dmitri with obvious interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.07,0:41:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The surge of possessiveness that hits
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.83,0:41:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,her is so powerful it stops her midstep.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.11,0:41:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The woman laughs at something Dimmitri
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.11,0:41:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,says leaning closer and Nell feels like
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.59,0:41:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,she can't breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.16,0:41:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What right does she have to feel jealous
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.76,0:41:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,when they're just roommates with
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.83,0:41:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,benefits?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.24,0:41:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But watching the stranger flirt with
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.07,0:41:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,him, seeing the easy charm in Dimmitri's
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.96,0:41:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,polite responses, Nell realizes with
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.07,0:41:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,startling clarity that she doesn't want
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.16,0:42:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to be just anything to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.44,0:42:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants to be everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.00,0:42:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The thought hits her like a freight
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.59,0:42:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,train. She's in love with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.28,0:42:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,When did that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.68,0:42:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,When did the mysterious man she'd
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.59,0:42:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,rescued become the person she can't
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.35,0:42:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,imagine living without?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.00,0:42:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Her mind is reeling with the magnitude
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.07,0:42:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,of her realization.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.04,0:42:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She's in love with a man whose real name
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.96,0:42:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,she doesn't even know. A man who might
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.68,0:42:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,see her as nothing more than temporary
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.68,0:42:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,shelter and convenient sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.59,0:42:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been somewhere else since the
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.96,0:42:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,coffee shop. Dimmitri observes on the
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.44,0:42:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,way home, his nostrils flaring slightly
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.83,0:42:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,as if he's reading her mood through
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.44,0:42:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.52,0:42:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine, just thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.00,0:42:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He studies her face for a long moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.40,0:42:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,then nods.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.40,0:42:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell you what, let me cook tonight. You
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.00,0:42:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,don't have to. I want to, he says
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.59,0:43:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,firmly, cupping her face in his hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.20,0:43:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me take care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.92,0:43:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,His thumb brushes across her lips and
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.80,0:43:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,she finds herself leaning into the touch
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.96,0:43:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,like she's drawn to him by some magnetic
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.11,0:43:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,force.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.44,0:43:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, she whispers.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.40,0:43:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He smiles slow, sharp, full of promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.59,0:43:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. I'll be back in an hour. She's
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.04,0:43:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,still standing there smiling to herself
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.44,0:43:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,when a harsh voice cuts through her
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.20,0:43:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.72,0:43:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be ashamed of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.44,0:43:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell spins around to see a well-dressed,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.59,0:43:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,middle-aged man striding toward her, his
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.31,0:43:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,face twisted with disgust. His expensive
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.68,0:43:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,suit and confident bearing scream money,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.31,0:43:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but his expression is filled with rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.59,0:43:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,"Excuse me," Nell says, taken aback.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.20,0:43:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"Being with that man," he says, his
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.56,0:43:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,voice getting louder.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.64,0:43:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you conveniently ignore all the lives
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.88,0:44:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,he's ruined because he buys you nice
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.88,0:44:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,things?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.96,0:44:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I don't know what you're
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.40,0:44:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,talking about. Blake Storm, the man
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.35,0:44:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,spits. CEO of Storm Industries.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.80,0:44:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell's frowns in confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.07,0:44:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb with me. I saw you with
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.16,0:44:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,him.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.92,0:44:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Nell shakes her head. Are you
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.11,0:44:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,talking about Dimmitri? Dimmitri? The
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.00,0:44:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,man scoffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.76,0:44:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You think I wouldn't recognize the man
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.68,0:44:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,who forced me to sell my company, then
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.59,0:44:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,gutted it, sold off the profitable
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.76,0:44:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,parts, and threw away the rest. Hundreds
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.24,0:44:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,of people lost their jobs because of
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.92,0:44:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,him.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.00,0:44:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you have the wrong person. Nell
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.56,0:44:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,protests. He's not some He's homeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.92,0:44:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He has amnesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.80,0:44:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Amnesia?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.56,0:44:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The man laughs harshly. The man's worth
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.28,0:44:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,millions. He's probably working some
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.52,0:44:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,elaborate scheme. tax evasion, hiding
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.07,0:44:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,assets, who knows what.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.96,0:45:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell remembers Dimmitri's wound, the
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.68,0:45:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,poor condition he'd been living in, and
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.76,0:45:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,above all the lost looks he'd get
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.07,0:45:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,whenever he tried to remember his past
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.24,0:45:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,life.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.48,0:45:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong, she insists, but doubt is
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.44,0:45:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,already creeping in. All those
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.07,0:45:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,contradictions about Dimmitri, his
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.31,0:45:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,refined speech, his business knowledge,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.35,0:45:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the way he commanded situations like he
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.83,0:45:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,was used to being in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.11,0:45:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go, she whispers.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.96,0:45:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, kid, the man says, his anger
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.40,0:45:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,fading into something like pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.59,0:45:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you truly didn't know, but now you
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.72,0:45:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,do. If I were you, I'd keep away from
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.76,0:45:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.44,0:45:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Chapter 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.83,0:45:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell sits at a wooden table at the
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.76,0:45:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,library surrounded by stacks of old
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.00,0:45:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,newspapers and magazines.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.28,0:45:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been at it for 2 hours combing
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.68,0:46:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,through back issues of the Wall Street
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.52,0:46:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Journal, Fortune, and Business Week.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.72,0:46:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Every search for Blake Storm brings up
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.28,0:46:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the same impossible truth. There he is
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.64,0:46:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,on Forb's 40 under 40. on a New York
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.92,0:46:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Times cover story, America's Youngest
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.31,0:46:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Billionaires, with a photo that makes
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.24,0:46:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,her stomach twist. Dimmitri in a sleek
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.11,0:46:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,suit, standing in a glasswalled office
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.52,0:46:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,high above Manhattan,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.68,0:46:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,accompanied by photos of his sprawling
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.83,0:46:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,estate in the Hamptons, his Manhattan
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.40,0:46:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,penthouse, his fleet of luxury cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.24,0:46:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell stares at the images, feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.72,0:46:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,smaller and more insignificant with each
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.96,0:46:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,one.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.88,0:46:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The man in these photos belongs to a
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.88,0:46:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,world so far removed from her cramped
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.20,0:46:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,one-bedroom apartment that they might as
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.52,0:46:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,well be different species.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.48,0:46:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The article describes his ruthless
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.40,0:46:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,business acumen and aggressive
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.07,0:46:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,acquisition strategies.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.40,0:46:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Storm Industries is based in Manhattan,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.11,0:47:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,nearly 3,000 miles from Seattle.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.20,0:47:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She buys the magazine and stumbles home.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.00,0:47:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Dimmitri is in the kitchen wearing
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.92,0:47:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,borrowed clothes, stirring a pot like he
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.72,0:47:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,belongs there. The sight guts her. Him
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.56,0:47:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,barefoot in her kitchen playing house
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.48,0:47:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,like it's real. Like any of this is
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.20,0:47:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,real.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.20,0:47:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell throws the magazine at him. It hits
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.76,0:47:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,his chest and falls to the floor, pages
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.31,0:47:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,spllaying open to reveal his face
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.24,0:47:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,staring up from the glossy cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.59,0:47:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The silence that follows is deafening.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.88,0:47:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Dimmitri stares down at the magazine and
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.04,0:47:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell sees the exact moment recognition
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.52,0:47:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,flickers across his features.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.80,0:47:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"Have you been lying to me?" she asks,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.40,0:47:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,her voice barely above a whisper.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.35,0:47:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,"Is this all some kind of joke?" "No,"
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.72,0:47:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,he protests immediately, shaking his
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.48,0:47:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,head. "Nell, I Blake Storm," she reads
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.40,0:48:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,from the cover. "Net worth 2.8 billion.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.40,0:48:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,CEO of Storm Industries." That's you,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.96,0:48:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.80,0:48:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dimmitri's mouth opens and closes like
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.88,0:48:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,he can't find the words.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.00,0:48:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I I don't remember any of that. He ends
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.76,0:48:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,up whispering.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.83,0:48:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A man came up to me today. Nell
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.24,0:48:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,continues. He knew you. He said you
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.35,0:48:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,destroyed his company.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.16,0:48:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.40,0:48:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Dmitri looks up from the magazine. I
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.20,0:48:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,would never.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.52,0:48:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at yourself, Nell says, gesturing
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.31,0:48:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to the open pages. Look at that house,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.24,0:48:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,that office. You could buy my entire
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.88,0:48:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,building with pocket change.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.83,0:48:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The photographs mock her with their
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.59,0:48:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,opulence.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.11,0:48:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She thinks of her own reflection in the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.88,0:48:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,bathroom mirror this morning. Tired
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.35,0:48:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,eyes, secondhand clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.80,0:48:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember being that person, he
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.11,0:49:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,insists, desperation in his voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.52,0:49:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter, Nell says, turning
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.00,0:49:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,away from him because looking at his
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.59,0:49:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,face hurts too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.48,0:49:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She feels like she's losing him, like
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.96,0:49:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,he's already slipping away into that
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.72,0:49:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,glittering world where she could never
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.48,0:49:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.40,0:49:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,"Now that you know who you are, you can
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.64,0:49:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,go home,"
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.40,0:49:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,she murmurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.04,0:49:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.55,0:49:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not going to stay here now, are
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.00,0:49:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,you?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.59,0:49:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She flips to the photo spread of his
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.35,0:49:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hampton's estate. Look at this. You
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.80,0:49:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,could be living in a mansion instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.59,0:49:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Dimmitri's voice becomes
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.24,0:49:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,strained. We don't even know if that's
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.31,0:49:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,really me. Could be a lookalike. Nell
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.11,0:49:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,shakes her head and moves past him
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.64,0:49:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,toward the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.11,0:49:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have dinner then, shall we? Oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.68,0:49:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,wait. Why would you have dinner here
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.59,0:49:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,when you could be dining at some
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.88,0:49:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Michelin starred restaurant within the
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.64,0:49:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,hour? Blake, that name means nothing to
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.20,0:50:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,me. He snaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.83,0:50:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That man said you were lying. Nell
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.16,0:50:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,continues that you're probably evading
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.72,0:50:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,taxes or hiding assets.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.24,0:50:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And you believed him? Dimmitri's voice
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.28,0:50:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,cracks. Just like that, some stranger on
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.24,0:50:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.92,0:50:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The pain in his voice makes her want to
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.76,0:50:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,take it all back, to apologize and
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.24,0:50:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,pretend none of this ever happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.04,0:50:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But she can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.52,0:50:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The photographs are right there, proof
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.76,0:50:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,of a life so far beyond her reach, it
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.00,0:50:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,might as well be fantasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.04,0:50:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Nell says, her voice small and
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.40,0:50:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,broken. I know you didn't lie about the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.40,0:50:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,amnesia, but the truth is it doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.80,0:50:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,matter. It's over this.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.48,0:50:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She waves between them. Can't go on
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.80,0:50:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.31,0:50:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And why not? Dimmitri challenges, tone
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.96,0:50:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,quiet. Because why would it? Why would
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.64,0:50:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,you choose this? She gestures around her
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.59,0:51:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,tiny apartment
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.59,0:51:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,when you could have that.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.48,0:51:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She holds up the photo of his estate,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.64,0:51:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the image blurring through her tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.68,0:51:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're not in there, Dimmitri
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.83,0:51:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,whispers, pointing at the pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.68,0:51:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.52,0:51:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They stare at each other across the
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.11,0:51:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,small space, the weight of unspoken
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.76,0:51:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,feelings hanging between them. Nell's
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.64,0:51:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,heart cracks a little more with each
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.31,0:51:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,passing second.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.88,0:51:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, you should go, she says finally.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.00,0:51:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Call your your company or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.28,0:51:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to. Yeah, well, I want you
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.40,0:51:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,to. You're in my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.68,0:51:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dimmitri's eyes flash gold. actually
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.72,0:51:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,flash like light reflecting off metal.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.00,0:51:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"You want me to leave?" he asks.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.52,0:51:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell doesn't reply. Can't trust her
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.00,0:51:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,voice. She's afraid if she speaks,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.80,0:51:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,she'll take it all back. Beg him to
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.88,0:51:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.64,0:51:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,"Nell."
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.80,0:52:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,His voice is rougher now with an edge
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.55,0:52:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,she's never heard before. It's almost a
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.35,0:52:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.68,0:52:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, she whispers, the word tearing
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.96,0:52:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,something vital inside her chest. I want
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.44,0:52:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.76,0:52:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Dimmitri looks like he might argue,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.68,0:52:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulder tense with tension, and then he
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.16,0:52:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,winces,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.16,0:52:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,his face contorting in pain, and
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.72,0:52:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly he stumbles, one hand going to
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.68,0:52:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,his chest like something inside is
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.00,0:52:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to claw its way out. "What's
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.04,0:52:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,wrong?" Nell asks, alarm cutting through
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.16,0:52:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,her anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.68,0:52:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't reply, just makes a sound
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.07,0:52:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,that's part gasp, part moan. His
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.28,0:52:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,breathing becomes labored and sweat
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.35,0:52:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,beads on his forehead despite the cool
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.68,0:52:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,evening air.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.24,0:52:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Dmitri.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.76,0:52:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear replaces her anger as she watches
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.76,0:52:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,him struggle. What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.72,0:52:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He crouches down, his whole body
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.20,0:53:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,trembling. His hands are clenched into
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.07,0:53:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,fists.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.80,0:53:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Dimmitri.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.48,0:53:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell's voice comes out as a whisper,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.55,0:53:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,terror replacing every other emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.40,0:53:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He makes a sound that's part grunt, part
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.88,0:53:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,growl, and then his bones begin to crack
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.68,0:53:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and stretch audibly.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.80,0:53:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark fur sprouts across his skin as his
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.44,0:53:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,clothes tear and fall away in tatters.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.55,0:53:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,His hands become claws. His teeth become
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.64,0:53:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,fangs. And his spine curves and extends
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.44,0:53:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,until where Dimmitri had been crouching,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.76,0:53:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,there's now a massive wolf with glowing
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.92,0:53:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,amber eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.55,0:53:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell screams, the sound ripping from her
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.96,0:53:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,throat involuntarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.07,0:53:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The wolf, Dimmitri, looks at her with
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.96,0:53:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,those familiar eyes for one
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.64,0:53:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,heartbreaking moment. Then he turns and
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.68,0:53:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,leaps through her window, shattering the
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.07,0:53:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,glass as he disappears into the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.40,0:54:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Chapter nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.31,0:54:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell stands frozen in her wrecked
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.24,0:54:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,apartment, surrounded by shattered glass
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.64,0:54:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and torn fabric, staring at the broken
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.35,0:54:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,window where Dimmitri disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.24,0:54:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The silence after the chaos is
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.16,0:54:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,deafening.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.55,0:54:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,First, gentle, mysterious Dimmitri is
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.59,0:54:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,actually a ruthless billionaire CEO, and
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.11,0:54:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,now he turned into a wolf right in front
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.55,0:54:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.48,0:54:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm losing my mind," she whispers,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.83,0:54:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,running her hands through her hair. "I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.40,0:54:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,actually losing my mind."
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.52,0:54:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She sees his face again right before the
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.59,0:54:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,shift. the confusion, the pain, and
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.28,0:54:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,afterward the way the wolf had looked at
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.52,0:54:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,her with such heartbreak.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.72,0:54:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She replays it again and again, the soft
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.07,0:54:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,whine when she screamed, the way he
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.72,0:54:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,flinched like her fear physically hurt
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.04,0:54:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,him.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.80,0:54:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"And now he's alone out there," she
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.04,0:55:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,says.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.64,0:55:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The thought jolts her. Dimmitri Blake,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.83,0:55:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,whoever he is, had been confused and
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.48,0:55:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,scared and she sent him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.31,0:55:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The guilt hits hard. She breathes,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.40,0:55:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,grabbing her jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.55,0:55:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She has to find him. Explain
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.31,0:55:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,something. She can't leave it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.52,0:55:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Not when she's in love with him. Not
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.00,0:55:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,after the way he looked at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.96,0:55:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The streets are eerily quiet for early
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.11,0:55:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,evening. Nell hurries toward the area
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.83,0:55:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,where she first found him, scanning
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.00,0:55:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,every alley, every shadow. Dimmitri,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.24,0:55:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,she calls softly, not wanting to draw
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.72,0:55:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,attention, but desperate for him to
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.31,0:55:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,hear. Dmitri, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.00,0:55:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She's halfway down the block when hands
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.76,0:55:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,grab her from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.16,0:55:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What? She starts to scream, but a rough
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.35,0:55:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,hand clamps over her mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.92,0:56:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She's yanked into the narrow space
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.76,0:56:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,between two buildings.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.07,0:56:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Her heart pounds as she struggles,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.31,0:56:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,biting the hand, kicking wildly. But
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.76,0:56:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,there are at least two men, maybe three,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.20,0:56:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.00,0:56:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Morrison, someone says behind her. Is
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.64,0:56:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that her?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.72,0:56:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Through the panic, she sees the man
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.88,0:56:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,who'd recognized Dmitri earlier step
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.20,0:56:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,from the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.76,0:56:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he says, eyeing her with something
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.11,0:56:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,close to pity. One of the men shoves a
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.68,0:56:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,watt of cash into Morrison's hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.31,0:56:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Payment as agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.55,0:56:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell's eyes widen.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.88,0:56:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She thrashes harder, tries to scream,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.76,0:56:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,but someone presses a cloth over her
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.76,0:56:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,nose and mouth. The chemical stench
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.55,0:56:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,makes her gag.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.04,0:56:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't worry," Morrison says, his voice
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.24,0:56:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,fading as the drug takes hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.11,0:56:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't hurt you. They just need bait
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.76,0:57:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to draw out Blake.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.64,0:57:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Chapter 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.04,0:57:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell wakes to a pounding head and the
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.28,0:57:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,bitter taste of chemicals in her mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.72,0:57:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She's zip tied to a metal chair in an
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.79,0:57:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,abandoned warehouse. The air thick with
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.59,0:57:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,rust and rot. Yellow street light
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.48,0:57:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,filters in through broken windows high
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.55,0:57:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,above.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.79,0:57:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Three men circle her like predators.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.44,0:57:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Big, muscular, too still. Something
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.31,0:57:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,about their movements reminds her of
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.92,0:57:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Dimmitri.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.00,0:57:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,She's awake, one says.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.20,0:57:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Another crouches to her eye level.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.11,0:57:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we wait for the alpha to come
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.96,0:57:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,running. The leader pulls a knife,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.68,0:57:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,testing its edge on his thumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.40,0:57:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, she's done her job. Morrison
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.52,0:57:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,said to make sure Blake suffers, didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.28,0:57:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,he?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.20,0:57:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Terror grips her as the blade comes
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.04,0:57:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.96,0:57:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Please
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.48,0:57:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,don't worry, sweetheart. We'll make it
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.40,0:58:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.31,0:58:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Then comes the growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.79,0:58:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Low, primal, inhuman. It vibrates
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.00,0:58:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,through the floor and up her spine. The
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.72,0:58:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,men freeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.88,0:58:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you said he didn't shift
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.40,0:58:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,anymore. One whispers.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.52,0:58:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up. Get ready. From the shadows, a
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.64,0:58:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,massive wolf steps into the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.20,0:58:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Bigger than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.28,0:58:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark fur like smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.00,0:58:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Amber eyes locked on the knife near her
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.64,0:58:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,throat. Well, well. The leader sneers,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.16,0:58:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,not lowering the blade. Look what
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.79,0:58:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,crawled out of the gutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.44,0:58:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The wolf steps forward. The men move,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.31,0:58:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,surrounding her. You remember how this
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.04,0:58:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,works, don't you? One more step and she
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.76,0:58:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.28,0:58:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Dimmitri stops, eyes locked on the
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.59,0:58:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,blade. Three shifters, one human shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.07,0:58:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's what you're going to do. You
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.92,0:59:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,shift back slow. Then we talk payback.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.35,0:59:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell sees the tension in his body. Rage
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.07,0:59:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,fighting restraint.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.31,0:59:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dimmitri, don't. The man backhands her.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.83,0:59:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Her head snaps sideways. Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.00,0:59:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when Dmitri snaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.55,0:59:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He lunges. Not at the leader, but the
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.11,0:59:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,man to his left. The element of surprise
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.00,0:59:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,gives him the edge. Teeth clamp down.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.20,0:59:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood sprays. Chaos erupts.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.79,0:59:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The leader turns, knife forgotten for a
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.20,0:59:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,breath. It's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.16,0:59:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Dimmitri releases his first target and
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.31,0:59:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,pivots toward Nell.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.64,0:59:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The third shifter starts to shift, but
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.96,0:59:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Dimmitri barrels through him like
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.55,0:59:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing, focused only on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.31,0:59:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The leader lifts the blade, but Dimmitri
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.40,0:59:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,slams into him. They crash into crates,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.59,0:59:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the knife clattering away.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.64,0:59:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All three men shift now, bones cracking,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.68,0:59:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,bodies stretching. But they're smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.88,1:00:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Dimmitri fights like something
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.40,1:00:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,possessed, wild, and precise.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.24,1:00:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They come at him in tandem, snapping at
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.24,1:00:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,his legs, trying to bring him down. The
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.79,1:00:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,floor runs with blood. Some his, most
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.72,1:00:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,theirs.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.55,1:00:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,One by one they falter, limping, beaten.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.40,1:00:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the leader remains.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.88,1:00:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He snarls, backing toward the window. He
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.16,1:00:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,vanishes into the dark.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.64,1:00:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Dimmitri sways. Blood mats his fur. He
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.83,1:00:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,takes one step toward Nell and
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.59,1:00:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,collapses.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.59,1:00:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Dimmitri.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.28,1:00:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell breaks free from the damaged
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.96,1:00:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,restraints and drops to her knees. His
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.35,1:00:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,form begins to shift.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.24,1:00:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Moments later, he lies naked and
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.07,1:00:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,bleeding on the concrete, pale, still.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.11,1:00:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dimmitri,"
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.04,1:00:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,she whispers, cradling his head. Her
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.92,1:00:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,hands press uselessly against the worst
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.07,1:01:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,of the wounds. "Wake up!"
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.52,1:01:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,His eyes flutter open, unfocused.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.28,1:01:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks at her, dazed.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.76,1:01:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"Nell, what happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.88,1:01:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember being angry and then
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.96,1:01:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ou didn't know she asks stunned about
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.16,1:01:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the wolf thing. You really didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.00,1:01:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He groans trying to sit then collapses
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.40,1:01:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,again.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.92,1:01:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Those men they knew me. They said you're
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.96,1:01:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,bleeding too much. Nell interrupts. I
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.76,1:01:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,need to get you help.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.24,1:01:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell, he whispers, his hand finding
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.11,1:01:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,hers. What if they're right? What if I
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.76,1:01:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,really am a monster?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.31,1:01:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, she says fiercely. The man I know is
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.59,1:01:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,good. He's kind. You just risked
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.40,1:01:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,everything to save me.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.79,1:01:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Her voice cracks. I love you, Dmitri.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.83,1:01:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever you were, whatever your name is.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.79,1:01:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,His eyes widen slightly at her
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.48,1:01:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,confession, but before he can respond,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.79,1:02:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,they roll back and he goes limp in her
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.96,1:02:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,arms.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.79,1:02:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Help! Nell screams into the empty
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.96,1:02:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,warehouse. Somebody help us.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.31,1:02:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when she hears the sound of
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.76,1:02:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,expensive cars pulling up outside,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.83,1:02:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,followed by rapid footsteps.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.72,1:02:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here, a voice calls out. Three
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.07,1:02:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,figures in tailored suits burst through
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.83,1:02:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the warehouse entrance, moving with the
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.00,1:02:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,same predatory grace as the men who'd
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.83,1:02:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,attacked them. But these newcomers scan
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.88,1:02:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the space with professional efficiency,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.04,1:02:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,their eyes immediately locking onto
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.79,1:02:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.72,1:02:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Alpha, the largest of the three, a man
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.59,1:02:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,with silver hair and cold blue eyes,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.92,1:02:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,rushes forward, dropping to his knees
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.68,1:02:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,beside them. Blake, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.76,1:02:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help us. Nell gasps. He's
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.16,1:02:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,bleeding out. We need to get him to a
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.83,1:02:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,hospital. Hospital. The woman in the
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.44,1:02:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,group, blonde and sharp featured, sneers
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.83,1:02:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,at Nell.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.52,1:02:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.52,1:03:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean what for? Nell asks.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.16,1:03:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He's dying.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.00,1:03:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The alpha doesn't need your human
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.59,1:03:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,hospital.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.11,1:03:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The third man, younger with wire- rimmed
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.24,1:03:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,glasses and a leather briefcase clutched
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.00,1:03:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,in his hands, says dismissively.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.44,1:03:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell tries to reach for Dmitri again,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.68,1:03:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,calling his name, but the silver-haired
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.24,1:03:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,man moves her aside.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.96,1:03:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Though, the one with the briefcase
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.55,1:03:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,continues. Maybe we could accelerate the
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.88,1:03:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,process a bit.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.96,1:03:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If he could make it to tonight's board
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.55,1:03:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,meeting, that would save us considerable
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.07,1:03:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,time. The shareholders are getting
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.92,1:03:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,restless.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.83,1:03:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,"These people are crazy," Nell mutters.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.64,1:03:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But then the woman produces a syringe
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.24,1:03:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,from her jacket and plunges it directly
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.92,1:03:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,into Dimmitri's chest. "No!" Nell yelps,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.48,1:03:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,but suddenly Dimmitri gasps and sits
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.31,1:03:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,upright, his eyes snapping open with
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.31,1:03:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,startling clarity. The three newcomers
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.20,1:03:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,immediately incline their heads in
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.79,1:03:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,perfect synchronization.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.03,1:03:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"Alpha," they say in unison.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.55,1:04:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back. The one with the briefcase
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.88,1:04:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,says, pulling out documents.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.68,1:04:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If I could just get your signature on
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.20,1:04:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,this merger agreement really quickly
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.31,1:04:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,for crying out loud. Nell explodes. He's
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.68,1:04:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,wounded. Leave him alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.72,1:04:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But Dimmitri blinks, takes a quick look
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.64,1:04:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,at the document, and his entire demeanor
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.72,1:04:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,shifts.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.79,1:04:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What the Malcolm? He snarls,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.28,1:04:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,ripping the papers to shreds. This
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.35,1:04:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,contract's absolute
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.31,1:04:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I tell you about doing business
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.76,1:04:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,with the Ford's group? You've got to
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.52,1:04:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,hold them by the balls, otherwise
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.88,1:04:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll bleed you dry.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.44,1:04:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Malcolm blinks back what might be tears
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.28,1:04:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,of relief.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.03,1:04:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank God you're back, Alpha. We've
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.44,1:04:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,been so lost without you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.16,1:04:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an incompetent git, Malcolm.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.40,1:04:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Dimmitri continues coldly.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.88,1:04:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But sir, where have you been? What
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.55,1:04:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,happened? We've been searching for
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.55,1:04:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,months.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.55,1:04:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,None of your business. Dmitri cuts him
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.96,1:04:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,off with icy precision. Isn't it your
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.52,1:05:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,job to know these things beforehand, not
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.35,1:05:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,ask stupid questions afterward?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.40,1:05:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The woman sniffs delicately.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.79,1:05:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Alpha, now that you've dealt with those
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.79,1:05:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,three, what should we do? Do we
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.55,1:05:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,retaliate? Make an example.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.76,1:05:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to send a message. The
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.59,1:05:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,silver-haired man agrees. Show the other
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.68,1:05:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,packs what happens when they target us.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.96,1:05:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell feels like she's watching
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.31,1:05:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,strangers. and she is because this cold,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.11,1:05:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,calculating man giving orders is not
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.11,1:05:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,someone she recognizes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.20,1:05:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the gentle person who read to
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.03,1:05:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,her in the evenings?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.96,1:05:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,"What do we do about the human?" the
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.96,1:05:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,woman asks suddenly, pointing at Nell.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.55,1:05:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Dimmitri's gaze snaps to her and for
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.72,1:05:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,just a moment, half a second, something
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.96,1:05:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,flickers across his face. "But then
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.64,1:05:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,escort her home," he says flatly. "Make
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.28,1:05:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,sure she signs the NDAs."
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.24,1:05:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Nell starts reaching for him, but
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.96,1:05:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,hands are already pulling her to her
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.48,1:05:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.00,1:06:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,As they lead her toward a waiting car,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.92,1:06:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell looks back desperately.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.79,1:06:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The man she fell in love with, gentle,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.28,1:06:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,lost Dimmitri, who made her coffee in
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.44,1:06:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the mornings and worried about Mr.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.44,1:06:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoffman, might as well have never
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.68,1:06:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,existed at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.72,1:06:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Epilog
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.40,1:06:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,2 weeks feels like 2 years. Nell stares
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.44,1:06:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,at her reflection in the bathroom
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.79,1:06:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,mirror, barely recognizing the woman
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.88,1:06:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,looking back. Dark circles, limp hair,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.00,1:06:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,an extra few pounds. The whole building
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.48,1:06:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,has been trying to feed her since since
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.88,1:06:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,he left. Even Mr. Ke brought cookies
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.40,1:06:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,hovering awkwardly in her doorway.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.44,1:06:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"We miss seeing you and Dmitri
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.11,1:06:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,together," Mrs. Chen had said gently.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.92,1:06:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,"Such a nice young man."
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.96,1:06:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell swallowed the lump in her throat.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.68,1:06:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you tell someone you're mourning
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.20,1:06:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,a man who might never have existed? He
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.76,1:06:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,disappeared without a word. Just a team
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.83,1:06:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,of lawyers at her door the next morning,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.83,1:06:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,armed with NDAs and confidentiality
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.00,1:07:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,agreements.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.16,1:07:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sign here and here. Initial here. A
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.76,1:07:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you for your discretion deposit
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.35,1:07:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,appeared in her account. Useful, yes,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.55,1:07:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,but it made her feel cheap. Erased.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.16,1:07:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a word from him. The one silver
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.79,1:07:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,lining, her job.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.52,1:07:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to Blake's resume overhaul, she
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.44,1:07:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,landed a position at a prestigious
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.96,1:07:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,marketing firm.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.96,1:07:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But success feels hollow when you have
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.72,1:07:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,no one to share it with. Her days blur
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.76,1:07:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,into meetings and emails. And tonight,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.24,1:07:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,walking home from another long day of
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.07,1:07:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,pretending to care. The sky opens up.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.48,1:07:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Rain pours in relentless sheets, the
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.88,1:07:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,same kind that brought them together.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.00,1:07:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Without thinking, her feet lead her
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.52,1:07:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,somewhere else, not home.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.07,1:07:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to the alley. It's smaller than she
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.88,1:07:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,remembers, dirtier, just a narrow
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.76,1:07:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,passage between buildings, unremarkable,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.64,1:07:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,except that it changed everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.68,1:07:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She stands in the exact spot where she
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.52,1:08:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,found him. Rain soaks through her
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.76,1:08:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,jacket.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.35,1:08:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How could she have known that the man
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.68,1:08:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,slumped here, lost, vulnerable, was a
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.64,1:08:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,corporate shark, a supernatural being?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.48,1:08:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet even then she'd felt something a
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.52,1:08:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,pull like he was already important.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.35,1:08:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Whereas she is just Nell dies ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.92,1:08:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl who happened to be in the wrong
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.60,1:08:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,place at the wrong time and had her
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.00,1:08:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,heart completely broken.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.79,1:08:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The rain suddenly stops hitting her,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.04,1:08:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,though she can still hear it pattering
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.56,1:08:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,around her. She blinks confused.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.79,1:08:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an umbrella over her head.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.92,1:08:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She turns slowly, afraid of what she'll
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.00,1:08:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,find, or worse, what she won't find.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.83,1:08:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's there, holding a black umbrella
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.67,1:08:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,over them both. His hair is shorter,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.64,1:08:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,expertly styled. He's clean shaven,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.35,1:08:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,dressed in a charcoal suit that probably
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.19,1:09:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,costs more than her rent, but his eyes,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.64,1:09:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,those unusual amber eyes with flexcks of
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.79,1:09:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,gold, are exactly the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.40,1:09:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still here?" he says softly, his
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.52,1:09:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,voice achingly familiar.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.40,1:09:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She shrugs, throat tight. "Yeah, well,"
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.67,1:09:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,she murmurs, "just in case." Something
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.96,1:09:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,like hope flickers across his face, but
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.88,1:09:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,she steals herself against it, against
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.19,1:09:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,him. The last time she saw this man, he
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.23,1:09:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,walked away without a backward glance.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.44,1:09:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"So," she says, finding her voice. You
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.44,1:09:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,remember everything then?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.08,1:09:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He hesitates.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.08,1:09:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he admits after a beat. I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.15,1:09:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. She gives him a small tight smile.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.64,1:09:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Convenient, I mean, for all those
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.96,1:09:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,business deals your associates seem to
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.64,1:09:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,need you for.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.79,1:09:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,His smile tightens into something
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.31,1:09:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,nervous.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.40,1:09:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he says. I suppose so. Rain drums
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.84,1:10:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,against the umbrella, creating a private
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.84,1:10:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,world around them. He looks at her
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.40,1:10:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,carefully.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.23,1:10:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"How have you been?" he asks.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.36,1:10:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,"Well, I haven't been kidnapped in a
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.52,1:10:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,while, so there's that." She replies,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.40,1:10:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,making him wse.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.71,1:10:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I am so deeply sorry for what
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.48,1:10:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,happened that night. It was entirely my
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.88,1:10:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,fault you got hurt. If I had known.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.56,1:10:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what hurt more than being
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.84,1:10:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,grabbed by those men? She interrupts.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.56,1:10:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the fact that you just disappeared
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.00,1:10:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,afterward without a word, without so
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.56,1:10:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,much as a goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.71,1:10:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Pain flashes across his face. "I'm
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.67,1:10:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,sorry," he says again. And she believes
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.71,1:10:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,he means it, which somehow makes it
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.56,1:10:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,worse. "When I woke up with all my
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.12,1:10:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,memories intact, I was concerned,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.48,1:10:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,alarmed, actually. How had I forgotten
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.96,1:10:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,everything? Who had done that to me?" He
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.44,1:10:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,runs a hand through his hair. I don't
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.15,1:10:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,have many friends, Nil, but I have
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.52,1:11:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,plenty of enemies. I wasn't even sure I
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.08,1:11:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,could trust my own pack. I needed to
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.08,1:11:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,understand what had happened before I
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.52,1:11:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,saw you again. And I
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.48,1:11:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He breaks off, reaching toward her face
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.64,1:11:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,before pulling his hand back.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.44,1:11:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to get you away from all of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.08,1:11:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I was afraid that if anyone suspected I
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.15,1:11:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,cared about you, they'd try to use you
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.32,1:11:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,against me again.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.36,1:11:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The sincerity in his voice touches
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.12,1:11:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,something in her, but she's been hurt
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.96,1:11:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,too badly to let her guard down easily.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.08,1:11:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You could have called. She sigh
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.15,1:11:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and risk someone listening in. When he
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.04,1:11:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,sees her surprised expression, he adds,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.67,1:11:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"Yes, turns out I'm a bit paranoid with
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.64,1:11:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,my memories back. I mean, comes with
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.96,1:11:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,being on top."
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.12,1:11:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"Right on top." She shakes her head. So,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.36,1:11:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you got your memories back and
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.64,1:11:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,remembered you're some big corporate.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.44,1:11:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I remembered I'm a lot of things, he
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.52,1:11:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,interrupts, and none of them
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.12,1:12:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,particularly good. His eyes darken. All
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.96,1:12:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,those things you heard about me that
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.23,1:12:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,night, they're true.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.36,1:12:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She reaches for him without thinking.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.52,1:12:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Her hand on his arm seems to calm him,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.76,1:12:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and he looks surprised at the contact.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.12,1:12:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's how I got cursed, he explains.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.32,1:12:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Cursed?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.84,1:12:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to lose my memories. It was a curse.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.88,1:12:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, magic? Nell asks. When he nods,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.92,1:12:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,she adds, "Magic is real."
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.67,1:12:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,His lips quirk in a small, almost amused
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.08,1:12:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,smile. "Well, how did you think I turned
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.71,1:12:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,into a wolf?" "Yeah, about that." She
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.71,1:12:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,hesitates. "Is that a regular thing you
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.28,1:12:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,can do?"
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.96,1:12:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,His smile falls again. "Yes," he says
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.32,1:12:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,carefully. I'm a shifter. I'm a man, but
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.12,1:12:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm also not. Or part of me isn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.80,1:12:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell thinks back to all the things that
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.40,1:12:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,had puzzled her about him. His acute
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.56,1:12:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,sense of smell. The way he'd sometimes
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.64,1:13:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,growl when frustrated. "Yeah," she says
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.84,1:13:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,slowly. "That kind of checks out." He
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.28,1:13:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,watches her reaction closely. "Does it
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.15,1:13:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,bother you?" Nell scoffs. "Is that why
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.92,1:13:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,you're here?" She snaps, worried I'll
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.48,1:13:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,tell someone your secret.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.19,1:13:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Dimmitri says quickly. I'm not
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.08,1:13:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,worried about that. I trust you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.12,1:13:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what are you worried about? He
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.60,1:13:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,takes a deep breath. You have to
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.08,1:13:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,understand that I'm not a good person,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.60,1:13:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell. Not really. That's why I got
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.92,1:13:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,cursed in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.48,1:13:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He continues before she can interrupt.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.28,1:13:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My ex- fiance, who I should confess I
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.64,1:13:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,only got engaged to in order to pressure
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.48,1:13:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,her family into signing a massive
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.00,1:13:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,business deal, cursed me after I broke
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.71,1:13:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,things off.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.64,1:13:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She had me kidnapped and dumped in this
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.40,1:13:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,city so no one would find me.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.19,1:13:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell makes a face and he pauses.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.00,1:14:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, she says. I'm just debating
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.12,1:14:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,whether you deserved it or not.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.00,1:14:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A surprised laugh escapes him. I
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.71,1:14:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,probably did, he admits. After getting
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.28,1:14:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,my memories back, I tracked down what
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.96,1:14:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheila had done.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.19,1:14:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The curse was designed to only break if
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.19,1:14:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,someone truly fell in love with me. Me
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.67,1:14:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,without my money or power or influence.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.40,1:14:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She was convinced it would never happen,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.48,1:14:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'd be stuck like that forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.60,1:14:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell feels heat rise to her cheeks. "Oh,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.19,1:14:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,when I was lying in this alley and you
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.28,1:14:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,found me, you said I remember what I
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.15,1:14:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,said." she interrupts, sighing.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.19,1:14:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks dejected at her tone, his
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.28,1:14:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulders dropping slightly.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.76,1:14:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,"Right," he says carefully. He
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.48,1:14:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,hesitates, then asks. "And now, do you
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.67,1:14:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,think perhaps in time you could still
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.15,1:14:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,love me now that I'm this?" He gestures
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.19,1:14:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,to himself.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.96,1:14:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,"This?" Nell repeats. "I'm still all
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.56,1:15:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,those terrible things I was before," he
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.28,1:15:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,says. Words coming faster now. I still
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.56,1:15:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,run a cut-throat company. I still make
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.88,1:15:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,decisions that hurt people. I'm still
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.36,1:15:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,surrounded by others just as ruthless as
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.19,1:15:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I am. But the thing is, Nell, that I now
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.88,1:15:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,remember what I was like when I was with
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.56,1:15:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you. And I liked that person much more.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.88,1:15:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Feeling herself blush, Nell snorts.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.08,1:15:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So what? You want me to be your moral
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.92,1:15:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,compass?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.52,1:15:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Nell.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.76,1:15:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,His voice drops.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.08,1:15:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to love me still. I've missed
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.96,1:15:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you. I can't go back to how things were
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.76,1:15:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,before.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.36,1:15:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.28,1:15:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Not when I know what it feels like to be
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.96,1:15:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,loved by someone like you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.67,1:15:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean poor and average? She jokes
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.84,1:15:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,weakly. I mean selfless, he says,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.84,1:15:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,reaching up to brush rainampened hair
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.67,1:15:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,from her face. And brave, kind.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.40,1:16:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,His thumb traces her cheekbone. And
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.88,1:16:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,very, very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.19,1:16:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nell feels tears building behind her
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.96,1:16:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,eyes, and she blinks them back
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.32,1:16:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,furiously.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.32,1:16:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"Look," she says, voice unsteady. "We
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.52,1:16:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,started this thing when you weren't
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.04,1:16:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,yourself. But your memories are back
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.60,1:16:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,now, and eventually you'll realize you
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.67,1:16:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,belong in that sparkly world of yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.23,1:16:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And I
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.15,1:16:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing sparkly about it," he
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.08,1:16:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,interrupts. "Not without you."
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.88,1:16:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,His lips find hers, warm and familiar
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.76,1:16:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and desperate all at once. He kisses her
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.56,1:16:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,like a drowning man finding air, like
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.04,1:16:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,someone coming home after a long
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.64,1:16:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,absence.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.71,1:16:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, he whispers. The curse broke
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.71,1:16:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,because you loved me when I had nothing
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.71,1:16:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,to offer but myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.52,1:16:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I have everything and the only thing
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.12,1:16:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I want is you. She looks up at him. This
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.88,1:16:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,man who is both Dmitri and Blake, both
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.19,1:16:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the lost soul she found in an alley and
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.60,1:16:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the powerful creature who stands before
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.36,1:17:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,her now.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.36,1:17:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a chance, he pleads softly. Just
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.92,1:17:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,one more chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.92,1:17:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And despite everything, despite the pain
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.08,1:17:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,of the past two weeks, despite the
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.84,1:17:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,complications that loving him will
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.36,1:17:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,bring, Nell rises on her tiptoes and
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.84,1:17:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,presses her lips to his again. The rain
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.96,1:17:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,continues to fall around them, but
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.71,1:17:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,neither notices.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.12,1:17:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,In this moment, in this unremarkable
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.28,1:17:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,alley where their story began, they are
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.67,1:17:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the only two people in the world. The
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.84,1:17:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,girl who found a wolf and the wolf who
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.48,1:17:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,found his heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.52,1:17:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for watching everyone. Leaving a
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.84,1:17:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,comment really helps support this video.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.76,1:17:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if you enjoyed the story, let me
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.67,1:17:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,know your favorite moment or quote in
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.28,1:17:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the comments below. I'll gift my
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.44,1:17:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,favorite response a free month access to
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.19,1:17:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,my Patreon where you'll find bonus
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.28,1:17:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,stories and exclusive scenes not shared
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.28,1:17:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,anywhere else. Hope to see you there
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.36,1:17:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,soon.
